---
title: Quick Ginger Braised Beef Stir-Fry with Shanghai Bok Choy
description: This dish is packed with all the flavours of Chinese takeout and comes together in just 20 minutes! Warm green onion-studded jasmine rice is the perfect vessel to sop up the salty-sweet garlicky sauce!
